00:21:07.701 --> 00:21:09.237
We had one girl competing,
though,

00:21:09.304 --> 00:21:10.674
and she managed to qualify.

00:21:10.740 --> 00:21:13.078
So that leaves us
with just one more guy.

00:21:13.145 --> 00:21:14.247
As for the girls,

00:21:14.314 --> 00:21:15.917
Miss Mitsui who's in
the final race

00:21:15.984 --> 00:21:17.654
will almost certainly
be qualifying.

00:21:18.255 --> 00:21:21.128
[Mayumi] We can't have Ah‐chan
letting up any time soon.

00:21:21.529 --> 00:21:22.531
<i>[Leonhard] Hmm.</i>

00:21:22.598 --> 00:21:23.900
<i>It might be a good idea for us</i>

00:21:23.967 --> 00:21:26.204
<i>to put more effort</i>
<i>into nurturing engineers</i>

00:21:26.271 --> 00:21:28.543
<i>at our school,</i>
<i>don't you think?</i>

00:21:29.945 --> 00:21:31.949
