as possible,

00:21:45.610 --> 00:21:46.779
so don't hold back.

00:21:47.681 --> 00:21:49.718
I feel no discomfort whatsoever.

00:21:49.785 --> 00:21:51.421
Actually,
it's such a perfect fit,

00:21:51.488 --> 00:21:52.825
it's almost creepy.

00:21:52.891 --> 00:21:54.562
‐ Is that right?
‐ [Shizuku] The others...

00:21:54.628 --> 00:21:56.398
‐ [gasps]
‐ The other two both won,

00:21:56.464 --> 00:21:57.500
didn't they?

00:21:57.568 --> 00:21:58.636
[Tatsuya] Yeah.

00:21:58.703 --> 00:22:01.341
Next is my turn for victory.

00:22:02.009 --> 00:22:03.245
No need to worry.

00:22:03.312 --> 00:22:04.615
If you perform
like you always do,

00:22:04.682 --> 00:22:06.351
there's no way you can't win.

00:22:07.153 --> 00:22:09.090
[grunts]
Of course I can

00:22:09.157 --> 00:22:11.529
since you've done everything
that's possible in order

00:22:11.596 --> 00:22:14.000
to pave the way to success
for me, Tatsuya.

00:22:14.434 --> 00:22:16.539
[Shizuku] All I have to do now
